Helper to generate configuration files for multi-instance ipcad(8)
==================================================================

It is intended to create configuration file(s) for ipcad(8) from
multiple fragments stored in netctl/etc/reipcad/data/<instance>/
and netctl/etc/reipcad/template/ and restart ipcad(8) service
with new configuration.

See netctl/etc/reipcad/ for more information about configuration
fragments and templates.
